        {
            "title": "滬深股指早市齊回吐 保險股受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美伊談判狀況未明，內地股市反彈兩日後於今早回吐，不少重磅板塊均現調整，內險股明顯受壓，中國人壽(02628)績後A、H齊跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國人壽官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20240425_FI_source-web_02628-8.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國人壽官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20240425_FI_source-web_02628-8.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國人壽官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早低開6點後於早市幾乎全程報跌，最高曾見3937點，僅升5點，於上午約10時開始持續「潛水」，低位3906點時跌25點，尾段一直在低位徘徊；滬指中午收報3909點，跌22點或0.58%，半日成交5305.92億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指早市相對跑贏，於初段出現的半日低位13723點時僅跌77點，但在高位13853點時也只升52點，今早基本呈窄幅爭持格局；深指中午收報13748點，跌52點或0.38%，成交6943.37億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也跌21點或0.47%，收報4516點；創業板指數則跌2點或0.07%，報3314點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國壽昨天收市後派成績表，業績符預期，該股今早卻反而裂口向下，國壽A股(601628.SH)挫5.19%，報37.44元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其他大型保險股同樣受壓，新華保險(01336)A股(601336.SH)跌3.74%，報64.11元；今日收市後公布業績的中國太保(02601)A股(601601.SH)也跌3.26%，報37.13元；同在今日收市派去年成績表的中國平安(02013)A股(601318.SH)則跌2.59%，報57.27元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15793655-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%87%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e9%bd%8a%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e4%bf%9d%e9%9a%aa%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-26 11:41:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
